      <title>德国金融监管机构警告称市场调整是最大风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/german-financial-watchdog-warns-market-corrections-top-risk-2025-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在科技股大幅下跌之后的第二天，德国监管机构联邦金融监管局 (BaFin) 表示，金融市场调整是其 2025 年关注的最大风险之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/german-financial-watchdog-warns-market-corrections-top-risk-2025-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 09:16:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行调查显示欧元区银行收紧企业信贷渠道</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/euro-zone-banks-tighten-companies-access-credit-ecb-survey-shows-2025-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周二公布的一项调查显示，欧元区银行上季度收紧了企业信贷渠道，并预计 2025 年前三个月将进一步收紧，这强化了在经济放缓之际进一步降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/euro-zone-banks-tighten-companies-access-credit-ecb-survey-shows-2025-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 09:09:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰计划进行数十年来最大规模的投资银行业务裁员</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-wind-down-ma-ecm-capabilities-europe-uk-americas-memo-shows-2025-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行周二表示，将逐步关闭其在欧洲、英国和美洲的并购和股票业务，这是该行几十年来最大规模的投资银行业务收缩，该行正加速向亚洲转移。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-wind-down-ma-ecm-capabilities-europe-uk-americas-memo-shows-2025-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 08:47:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲银行可能难以再现强劲的年终业绩</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/european-banks-may-find-it-tough-repeat-strong-end-of-year-performance-2025-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计欧洲银行将报告去年最后三个月的利润大幅增长，这得益于贷款利润率依然强劲以及投资银行收入丰厚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/european-banks-may-find-it-tough-repeat-strong-end-of-year-performance-2025-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰银行 ING 与投资者达成协议后退出俄罗斯</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ing-groep-sell-russian-business-global-development-jsc-2025-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰银行 ING Groep 周二表示，已达成协议，将其在俄罗斯的业务出售给当地公司 Global Development JSC，这使该银行的风险敞口达到 10 亿欧元（10.4 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/ing-groep-sell-russian-business-global-development-jsc-2025-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 06:52:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪警告称，欧洲放松抵押贷款规则将增加贷方的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/looser-mortgage-rules-europe-raise-risks-lenders-warns-moodys-2025-01-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[信用评级机构穆迪周二表示，欧洲多个国家推出的宽松抵押贷款规则增加了贷款违约的风险，并对银行的长期信用状况产生负面影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/looser-mortgage-rules-europe-raise-risks-lenders-warns-moodys-2025-01-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 06:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
